description.displayText: Balbina did not show up to her scheduled and confirmed interview. She left me waiting needlessly. By doing so, took the opportunity away from someone else who could have been interviewed. While she comes across very professional and enthusiastic on the phone, she clearly is not responsible enough to cancel an interview appointment.
